<item>
            <title>[SOLR-9710] SpellCheckComponentTest (still) occasionally fails</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-9710</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In December 2015, I addressed occasional, non-reproducable failures with the Spellcheck Component tests.  These were failing with this warning:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;PERFORMANCE WARNING: Overlapping onDeckSearchers=2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...and the test itself would run before the test data was committed, resulting in failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This problem is re-occurring and needs a better fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
